{"tid":1043167,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百人瘋搶$12自助早餐　又食又拎嚇窒老闆","createTime":"2019-03-02T05:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T15:18:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebaf9ad6e6d38d5432550dedd1662e98fded53c7","tid":1043167,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190301/large/1551455735_4823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190301%2Flarge%2F1551455735_4823.jpg&h=35c04c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食客爭搶米粉，連湯勺也出動。<br />\n<br />\n內地人為慳十元八塊搶食的場面有多恐怖，相信連同胞也難以忍受！廣西南寧一間酒樓，近日推出每位10元人民幣（下同；約11.7港元）的自助早餐大優惠，結果引起一群瘋狂食客光顧，他們毫不顧禮儀，如同餓鬼、蝗蟲般哄搶食物。酒樓昨日已將收費恢復為每位19元（約22.2港元），並訂立規定，老闆直言現在已無人哄搶了。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的酒樓名為「大英雄長湖酒樓」，2000年曾獲得「敬老飯店」的稱號。酒店方面在上月25日起推出自助早餐，特別在頭3日以每位10元的「試業價」，優惠一眾經常光顧的中老年顧客及上班族。老闆說，原本預計只有2至3枱食客，沒想到最後竟來了很多人，將可以容納300人的大廳擠得水洩不通。部份客人還不顧安全，如同飢民般猛搶食物，更有人又食又打包，十分誇張。<br />\n<br />\n酒樓方面見形勢不妙，隨即調整策略，包括實施顧客實名制購票，並增加食物供應，以及向部份老人細心講解自助餐不允許打包的規則。至昨日，酒店結束10元優惠，改為食客若出示老人卡，便可以16.9元的價格享用自助早餐，其他食客則一律收19元正價，才沒有再出現搶食的情況。<br />\n<br />\n梨視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190302/59319292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59319292&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWvZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=b4c4ec60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59319292&h=da2a539e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190302/59319292</a>"},{"pid":"a185d6fbb9043bc33d159ba13af58a37b4ca6052","tid":1043167,"uid":25676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d923cde6f8e891880d660ec10f641eca614dbf5","tid":1043167,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d747922654a74a90d5c8a425d3e0c562e499aae7","tid":1043167,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"喺大陸預咗"},{"pid":"0cb9411ab35bdf17fd67450ff75117c06e4d9f27","tid":1043167,"uid":102222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"貴少少就唔食<br />\n支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedb86837b178a2bb1a816c2a64b8bf3c90100db","tid":1043167,"uid":166709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cb9411ab35bdf17fd67450ff75117c06e4d9f27","tid":1043167,"uid":102222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"貴少少就唔食<br />\n支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"貴少少唔食冇問題wor, 本身都唔方好野。 問題係佢地個食相太柒姐"},{"pid":"8b344701bde1081b9ab86929b99793c5fcbe2510","tid":1043167,"uid":23200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"廢老飯店炸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}